items.title: 'The danger is not over in Pakistan' after flash floods
items.description: Emergency teams searching for the missing are struggling through mud and debris, following flash flooding in Khyber Pakhtunkhwa province.

items.title: Two summits later, Trump still faces tough obstacles in quest for peace in Ukraine
items.description: Meetings in Alaska and Washington were high on pomp and low on breakthroughs, but there were two potentially significant developments.

items.title: Kremlin plays down Zelensky talks as Trump warns Putin may not 'want to make deal'
items.description: The US president conceded the war in Ukraine was "tough to solve" after several days of high-level talks.

items.title: Israel demands release of all Gaza hostages, casting doubt on ceasefire proposal
items.description: It comes a day after Hamas said it accepted a proposal for a 60-day truce, during which around half of the 50 hostages would be freed.
